## Commercial License

### When Required

A Commercial License is required for any use that is primarily intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation, including but not limited to:

- Selling tablets, phones, or devices with GridDown pre-installed
- Bundling GridDown with SDR hardware, survival kits, or other products
- Deploying GridDown across a business or enterprise
- Offering GridDown as part of a paid service or subscription
- Government, defense, or military deployment
- White-label or OEM distribution under your own brand

### License Tiers

| Tier | Description | Starting Price |
|------|-------------|----------------|
| Startup | Small business (<$1M revenue), up to 100 units/year | $2,500/year |
| Business | Mid-size business, up to 1,000 units/year | $10,000/year |
| Enterprise | Large deployments, unlimited units | $25,000/year |
| OEM/White-Label | Custom branding, redistribution rights | Contact Sales |
| Government | Federal, state, local government use | Contact Sales |

*Prices are indicative. Contact licensing@blackdot.tech for a custom quote.*

### Commercial License Benefits

- Rights to distribute GridDown with hardware products
- No copyleft requirements on your proprietary additions
- Priority technical support
- Early access to new features
- Custom feature development (Enterprise+)
- Indemnification against IP claims
- Multi-year discount options

### How to Obtain

1. Email licensing@blackdot.tech
2. Describe your use case and expected volume
3. Receive a custom quote
4. Execute agreement and submit payment
5. Receive license certificate

